          "explanation": "P. malariae which attacks mainly senescent (old) RBC’s: Agent of Quartan malaria\nP. ovale and P. vivax: attack younger RBCs and reticulocytes: Agent of benign tertian malaria\nP. falciparum: attacks RBC of all ages: Agent of malignant tertian malaria."
