          "id": "medmcqa-44951bf6-36b2-4283-b511-3075505c9e1b",
          "text": "A chest physician performs bronchoscopy in the procedure room of the out patient depament. To make the instrument safe for use in the next patient waiting outside, the most appropriate method to disinfect the endoscope is by -",
