          "explanation": "Leptospirosis\nLeptospira organisms are found in damp environments and affect people working there, like\n\nStagnant water (sewer workers)\nWet soil (agricultural workers)\nMine workers\n\nInfected person can develop mild febrile illness, headache to jaundice and renal failure. Human acts as an end host of these organisms."
