          "id": "medmcqa-14a9d171-cee5-4ffa-a67c-f2e441af2daa",
          "text": "A young girl has had repeated infections with Candida albicans and respiratory viruses since the time she was 3 months old. As pa of the clinical evaluation of her immune status, her responses to routine immunization procedures should be tested. In this evaluation, the use of which of the following vaccines is contraindicated?",
