          "id": "medmcqa-b4eeef3f-5a13-4599-840c-b961c12c1eea",
          "text": "Amniocentesis conducted during genetic counseling of a pregnant woman reveals a fetal adenosine deaminase deficiency. This autosomal recessive immunodeficiency is usually associated with which of the following?",
