          "correctOptionId": "opt-2",
          "explanation": "Lymphoreticular system include lymphoid & reticular components, with clearly demarcated function. The lymphoid cells lymphocytes & plasma cells are primarly concerned with specific immune response. The phagocytic cells, forming pa of the reticuloendothelial system are primarly concerned with the scavenger functions Reff: Ananthanarayanan & Paniker's textbook of microbiology 9th edition pg: 128",
