          "correctOptionId": "opt-1",
          "explanation": "There are two known species of Pneumocystis - Pneumocystis carinii, commonly found in rats and Pneumocystis jirovecii seen in humans. Ref: Textbook of Microbiology, Ananthanarayan and Paniker; 9th edition",
