          "explanation": "Ans. is None In salmonella gasteroenteritis:- i) Diarrhea is nonbloody (option a is incorrect). ii) It is due to invasion of bowel mucosa, not toxin mediated (option b is incorrect). iii) It is diagnosed by isolation of organism from stools (option c is incorrect). iv) Fever is one of the commoner symptom (option d is incorrect)."
