          "id": "medmcqa-e2c1b557-7332-4a6a-a8e3-c763c0481bf2",
          "text": "An HIV-positive patient with a viral load of 100,000 copies/mL of HIV RNA and a drop in his CD4 T-cell count from 240 to 50mL has been diagnosed with Pneumocystis jiroveci pneumonia. Which of the following is the best description of the stage of this patient's HIV disease?",
